OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with sunny spells to start.
OL,6,FShowers in the far north fading. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill increase, with rain spreading
OL,8,Finto western areas later, bringing
OL,9,Fstrengthening winds and coastal gales,
OL,10,Fsevere in the far northwest.
OL,11,FTemperatures near average, colder
OL,12,Fnorthwest overall conditions.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain in the west, locally
OL,15,Fheavy at first, edging eastwards.
OL,16,FClear spells and blustery showers
OL,17,Ffollow in the west, turning chilly
OL,18,Fwith local rural frost as winds ease
OL,19,Fin places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
