OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRain across central and
OL,6,Fwestern areas, but clearing eastwards.
OL,7,FShowers follow, heavy in Northern
OL,8,FIreland and western Scotland. Windy
OL,9,Fwith coastal gales in the west.
OL,10,FTemperatures near seasonal average.
